<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" style="border: none;background-color: #F8F9FA;margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

	<title>Recover Password</title>
</head>
<body style="border: none;background-color: #F8F9FA;margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">
	<div class="mailContentContainer" style="text-align: center;">
		<div class="spacer" style="height: 50px;">&nbsp;</div>

		<div class="imageContainer">
			<img src="cid:logo" alt="IMMPC">
		</div>

		<div class="mainContent" style="margin: 0;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top: 45px;text-align: center;max-width: 600px;height: auto;">
			<p class="first" style="text-align: start;margin: 0;height: 27px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;color: #6E6B7B;margin-bottom: 15px;">Buen día <span class="bold" style="font-weight: bold;">{{ name }}</span>,</p>
			<p class="second" style="text-align: start;margin: 0;height: 27px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px;line-height: 27px;color: #6E6B7B;margin-bottom: 18px;">Aquí está tu código para reestablecer tu contraseña:</p>

			<table style="width: 194px;text-align: center;margin: 0;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 23px;">
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td><span class="number" style="height: 75px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 50px;line-height: 75px;color: #1A1D45;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">{{code1}}</span></td>
						<td><span class="number" style="height: 75px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 50px;line-height: 75px;color: #1A1D45;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">{{code2}}</span></td>
						<td><span class="number" style="height: 75px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 50px;line-height: 75px;color: #1A1D45;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">{{code3}}</span></td>
						<td><span class="number" style="height: 75px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;font-size: 50px;line-height: 75px;color: #1A1D45;margin-left: 10px;margin-right: 10px;">{{code4}}</span></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>

			<p class="caption" style="text-align: start;margin: 0;height: 27px;font-style: italic;font-weight: 300;font-size: 14px;line-height: 21px;color: #6E6B7B;">Si no solicitaste un restablecimiento de tu contraseña, puedes ignorar este correo electrónico.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="spacer last" style="height: 150px;">&nbsp;</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
